{"tid":1798313,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"811關節擊碎 設計師盼眾籌追究","createTime":"2019-12-26T06:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T07:14:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"73a55184b69565f6ab28623bc7799355f6432d6f","tid":1798313,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"警方8月11日在銅鑼灣派出喬裝警員行動，從事設計的林維坤稱被喬裝警從後推倒，疑猛力撞擊致左肩關節脱骱、關節位碎開4塊，手術後留下11厘米長疤痕，需觀察6至9個月才能確定有無骨枯的後遺症。<br />\n<br />\n難以抬高左手，要定期針灸放血<br />\n<br />\n林維坤先被送往新屋嶺扣留中心，由受傷到送院前後擾攘6小時。他目前難以抬高左手，要定期針灸及放血，形容經歷「無妄之災」，但相對爆眼、中槍等傷勢，已算「好輕微」。他說反修例運動令他接觸到記者、青年等不同類型的人，受重傷亦無悔，期望眾籌、以法律途徑追究警暴，「光明正大打倒」警察。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20191226/s00006/6f6a6ba4dd563b035f4c956858b61a44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20191226%2Fs00006%2F6f6a6ba4dd563b035f4c956858b61a44.jpg&h=10b42f12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7596b0275f025a1dc88d8f0277a7d07e4b30e76b","tid":1798313,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"期望眾籌、以法律途徑追究警暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等你"},{"pid":"aa47ece0343f52877c11345f630d31473c77be29","tid":1798313,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"叫佢搵民陣或許智峯<br />\n大家都係做緊同一樣野<br />\n唔好分散攪眾籌"},{"pid":"9ae674ba536dc7d3db06dfd10c1ce1b971751857","tid":1798313,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:52:49.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"30ffa7a72e0682068f11c617d262c7a6e253ece2","tid":1798313,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"支持你<br />\n<br />\n告尻佢地啦"},{"pid":"ca8e8c1d590b408d08b74dd46e3071a8c6e63015","tid":1798313,"uid":61615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/citmYQt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/